<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <%- include('bootstrap') %>
        <style>
            body {
                display: flex;
                min-height: 100vh;
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .content {
                flex-grow: 1;
            }

            .iframe-container {
                max-width: 560px;
                aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
            }

            /* Then style the iframe to fit in the container div with full height and width */
            .responsive-iframe {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
            }
        </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('navbar') %>
        <div class="container content mt-3 mb-3">
            <h1>Leadership</h1>
            <div class="accordion mt-3" id="accordionExample">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed shadow-none" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                            Aggie Coding Club - Workshop Officer OIT
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p><b>Aggie Coding Club : 8/22 - 12/22</b></p>
                            <p>
                                I am currently a Workshops Officer OIT (officer in training). I am designing fun and
                                useful computer science workshops for the Aggie Coding Club. These workshops will be
                                held in the Fall 2022 semester.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingNine">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed shadow-none" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseNine" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseNine">
                            TAMU ASLA Website - Scrum Master
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseNine" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingNine"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p><b>TAMU ASLA Website Team : 1/22 - 5/22</b></p>
                            <p>
                                While working on the TAMU ASLA Wesbite, I served as the scrum master in a team of 6.
                                Some of my duties included leading the daily stand-ups and the sprint
                                retrospectives. You can read more about the TAMU ASLA Website on the <a href="/projects"
                                    class="link-primary">projects
                                    page</a>.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('footer') %>
</body>

</html>